<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī śakavarṣaṁbulu 1423 A 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>gunēṁṭi durmmati saṁvatsara śrāvaṇa 
<lb n="3"/>śu 5 <unclear>śu</unclear> śrīraṁgarājulavāri kō 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>bhūmilōni ciṁtalapūṁḍina ka 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>raṇaṁ nāvayya tama toṁbhuṭi 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>na rāghavayyakuṁ buṇyamugānu 
<lb n="7"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> hanumaṁttuni pratiṣṭhacēsi dēvaḷini <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/>śrīmatē <unclear>rā</unclear>mānujāyanamaḥ 
